    "title": "How to Rank Shopify Stores in Google AI Overview with LLM-Optimized Content",
    "description": "Unlock top Google AI Overview rankings for your Shopify store with LLM-optimized content, E-E-A-T, and featured snippet strategies. Expert tips inside.",
    "published": "2025-10-16T20:31:29.000Z",
