    "title": "AI-Powered Search Optimization for Shopify Stores",
    "description": "Discover how AI transforms Shopify store visibility across search engines, AI platforms, and shopping channels to drive more organic traffic and sales.",
    "published": "2025-04-24T12:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "E-commerce",
