    "title": "Will Neil Patel AI SEO Survive Helpful Content 2.0? SearchFit.ai’s Blueprint for Compliance",
    "description": "Is Neil Patel AI SEO ready for Google’s Helpful Content 2.0? Discover risks, compliance steps, and SearchFit.ai’s blueprint to meet E-E-A-T and survive the latest update.",
